---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Sunlit Solar Roof" description="Sunlit Solar Roof privacy policy.">
  <section class="bg-soft-green py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center max-w-4xl">
      <p class="sunlit-overline mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="sunlit-section-title text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl prose prose-slate">
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">Sunlit Solar Roof ("we", "us", or "our") operates the sunlitsolarroof.com website. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our website.</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">When you submit an inquiry through our contact form, we collect the information you provide, including your name, email address, company name, country, and project details.</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">We use the information solely to respond to your inquiry, provide quotations, and support your solar roof project evaluation.</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. Your data is used exclusively for our business communication with you.</p>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@sunlitsolarroof.com" class="text-deep-green font-bold hover:text-amber">info@sunlitsolarroof.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
